"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/1823.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 710px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 15px\">DVI 影像传输介面可传送未经压缩的影像资料, 并且最佳化数位显示设备的画面品质, 例如 LCD 萤幕, 数位投影机等. 此外, DVI介面也和HDCP(High-bandwidth Digital Content Protection)相容.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px \'arial verdana helvetica sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 20px\">支持On/Off Charge功能</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 160px; padding-right: 20px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\"><img title=\"支持On/Off Charge功能\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/1668.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 710px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 15px\">藉由技嘉独特USB 3倍电力供应设计，并搭配最新ON/OFF Charge技术，除了可提供iPhone手机装置，还包括iPad及iPod touch等目前广受欢迎的手持装置，不仅在计算机开机或关机都能随时提供充电，更支持快速充电，节省高达40%的充电时间，让您随时需要，即可随时使用。...<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"line-height: 20px; font-family: \'arial verdana helvetica sans-serif\'; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold\">more</a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<font color=\"#ff0000\">*由于某些手机装置的规格限制，使用非On/Off Charge的USB端口时，在系统进入S4/S5状态前请先将手机连接于系统。手机快充情形，可能会依据不同机种而有所不同。</font>&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"line-height: 20px; font-family: \'arial verdana helvetica sans-serif\'; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"On/Off Charge Driver download\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/FileUpload/Features/2/Photo/1740.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"65\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px \'arial verdana helvetica sans-serif\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/images/line_hr.png\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 900px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(29,108,254); font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 20px\">支持ErP Lot 6</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 160px; padding-right: 20px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\"><img title=\"支持ErP Lot 6\" src=\"http://www.gigabyte.cn/fileupload/features/2/overview/60.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 0px; width: 710px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 15px\">ErP全名为能源相关产品(Energy-related Products) ，属于欧盟环境保护法令的